seo: 通达OA,漏洞检测,在线用户登录漏洞,auth_mobi.php
seo_en: Tongda OA,vulnerability detection,online user login vulnerability,auth_mobi.php
summary: 该插件用于检测通达OA v11.7版本中auth_mobi.php文件的在线用户登录漏洞，通过发送特定请求判断是否存在漏洞并输出相关信息。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the online user login vulnerability in the auth_mobi.php file of Tongda OA v11.7. It sends specific requests to determine if the vulnerability exists and outputs relevant information.
